flowchart TB
    N1["1. neo-n4-sdk: Trust boundary shows what must be proven rather than believed."]
    N2["2. Trusted base: configuration policy, signing policy, target-network profile"]
    N3["3. Untrusted input: developer app | gateway endpoint | wallet/config"]
    N4["4. Validation boundary: config, params, signing, network, and output format validate"]
    N5["5. Replay and ordering: request id, network id, and signing domain prevent duplicate or cross-network use"]
    N6["6. Authority: signatures bind network, account, action, and validity period"]
    N7["7. External systems: gateway, wallet, node RPC, developer environment"]
    N8["8. Observed evidence: command, config digest, network, output artifacts, and diagnostics"]
    N1 --> N2
    N1 --> N3
    N1 --> N4
    N1 --> N5
    N1 --> N6
    N1 --> N7
    N1 --> N8
    N2 -. constrains .-> N4
    N4 -. produces .-> N5
    N5 -. consumed by .-> N6
